</h3><p class="sc-ZOtfp cLnRKw pf-49_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Innovators are the first individuals to adopt a new idea or technology. They are risk-takers, adventurous, and willing to invest time and resources in unproven innovations.
